summary: This mod adds a Npc of Foxwell in the market place of Whiterun.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a Npc of Foxwell in the market place of Whiterun. Foxwell doesn't do anything at all... He walks around the market place of Whiterun doing shit all.
